MC section where they talk about Melbourne's attractions like art, food, and coffee.
Baelz notices a fan with a specific sign/fanart in the crowd and reacts to it.
The duo announces the end of the free preview and encourages viewers to buy tickets.
End card for the free preview stream with static text in Japanese and English.
